Description: Handle of pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.31, 32. From the same die as Alexandria, Greco-Roman Museum, ABC 0919.18.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0513)
